description: Minor material amendment (S.73) to vary condition no.2 (approved plans), seeking to allow changes on the restaurant design, in pursuant to planning permission reference  P/2013/4366 dated 18/07/2014 for'' Application for a new planning permission to replace extant planning permission P/2010/2515 dated 23/09/2010 for Refurbishment and extension of the existing Shooting Club Lodge with new earth mounding for the provision of additional overflow spaces to provide a new workshop (72sqm), groundstaff welfare facilities (365sqm), new office accommodation (60sqm), new foyer, provision of a new restaurant, kitchen and support facilities to accommodate up to 120 people (195 sqm), adaptation of the existing clubhouse and dedicated club lounge (83sqm) and  adaptation of the second floor of the clubhouse to provide two flats for staff (Please see planning application ref: P/2010/2515 for plans and supporting information)''
